{"tid":1993852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷俄關係緊張　布拉格市長認受暗殺威脅","createTime":"2020-04-29T05:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T10:22:26.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da9e70bfe7a98422404f62cda39d851240c562b1","tid":1993852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:21:17.000Z","msg":"捷俄關係緊張　布拉格市長認受暗殺威脅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/04/blog-post_29.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F04%2Fblog-post_29.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=0df4c18e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/04/blog-post_29.html</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克跟俄羅斯的關係近日轉趨緊張，捷克週報Respekt星期日（26日）披露，首都布拉格的市長賀瑞普（Zdenek Hrib）面對暗殺威脅後，賀瑞普自己昨天（28日）親口證實，他正受警方嚴密保護。賀瑞普不肯說出加強保安的理由，但Respekt及其他中歐傳媒指出，這是因為俄羅斯派了特工，企圖暗殺賀瑞普。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賀瑞普只表示，他近日覺得被人跟蹤，多次在家附近見到同一個人，向警方報案後，警方決定加強保護他。但他沒說，加強保安與他報案，是否有關連。<br />\n<br />\n根據Respekt及其他捷克傳媒報導，捷克掌握到情報，一名俄羅斯特工假扮成俄國外交官入境，並帶了蓖麻劇毒，捷克情報部門認為該人對賀瑞普及布拉格第6區市長Ondrej Kolar構成嚴重威脅，因此近日派出貼身保鑣，保護二人。<br />\n<br />\n賀瑞普之前支持把俄國駐捷大使館前的廣場，改為以遭暗殺的俄羅斯反對派人士湼姆佐夫（Boris Nemtsov）命名。至於Kolor，他本月支持把布拉格內的蘇聯將領Ivan Konev的塑像拆走，Konev是二戰蘇軍英雄，在俄羅斯備受尊崇，但他也曾鎮壓1956年匈牙利革命和1968年布拉格之春，因此不少捷克人抗拒國內有Konev的塑像。這兩件事都惹怒俄羅斯，因此令人懷疑俄國想向二人下毒手。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯已經否認報導，批評這是抹黑俄羅斯，俄羅斯才是事件中的受害者。"},{"pid":"d0416a6d7ef008ac6c0ef93a796ccd8dce26b996","tid":1993852,"uid":133086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"捷克呢排咁搶口啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(唔知wow左未) 捷克有8964天安門資訊比大陸人睇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1991039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1991039</a>"},{"pid":"33d59d7736c8e7512d52febcb5e193d155a11489","tid":1993852,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"俄佬有冇咁玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f7f05949eb78034f98a5f1b15860f6d87d6e25","tid":1993852,"uid":61589,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"斐迪南刺殺2.0<br />\n真係WW3味濃.............<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f739be280a12cdaab326224d21418efe50e0d9f","tid":1993852,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d59d7736c8e7512d52febcb5e193d155a11489","tid":1993852,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"俄佬有冇咁玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6b8c6cafd6f49fdca206ec74f25325099be16d","tid":1993852,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"捷克週報Respekt<br />\nRespect??"},{"pid":"c9e573cee02d87f9b0dd43b552244df9ab81981f","tid":1993852,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:45:17.000Z","msg":"好怕佢好似當年喺英國個俄國人咁死得不明不白"},{"pid":"2102764566dd71703e2544f3c00ac774065790b1","tid":1993852,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33d59d7736c8e7512d52febcb5e193d155a11489","tid":1993852,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"俄佬有冇咁玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"中國大使逼死捷克參議院長？訪台前夕猝死，遺族控訴的「密室恐嚇信」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n契哥契弟一脈相承"},{"pid":"83b8a919d2fb01a57c6473af3c0625208a534c4e","tid":1993852,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"支那同俄羅斯想搞掂曬捷克親台親美派"},{"pid":"d64e3e266748eea23ecc57ff58a53c6f